addPassportLogic(string,address).details: Registers a new passport version with its logic implementation address

params._implementation: representing the address of the new passport logic implementation to be registered
params._version: representing the version name of the new passport logic implementation to be registered

getCurrentPassportLogic().details: Tells the address of the current passport logic implementation
getCurrentPassportLogic().return: address of the current passport logic implementation

getCurrentPassportLogicVersion().details: Tells the version of the current passport logic implementation

getPassportLogic(string).details: Tells the address of the passport logic implementation for a given version
getPassportLogic(string).return: address of the passport logic implementation registered for the given version
